name: Ambra Battilana Gutierrez
description:
Ambra Battilana Gutierrez (born 15 May 1992) is a Filipino-Italian model who was a finalist for Miss Italy and has been featured in GQ Italy. Gutierrez is a member of the Model Alliance’s Leadership Council, which aims to help create a safe and fair work environment for other models, and works closely with organizations like Eek Media, Safe Horizon, and Humanility.

If you like my work, a review is more than welcome! Also, follow me on Twitter or Instagram!

Looking for something... spicy? Here's my Patreon!

Also, I recently started a blog where I will gather resources and tutorials about my work here!

My third job here is a textual inversion of the wonderful Ambra Battilana Gutierrez. Made with 3000 training steps and 30 public images of her. I am particularly satisfied with this one! To use it:

  • download the file and place it into stable-diffusion-webui>embeddings folder

  • Then simply add amgutierrez to your prompt and enjoy!

  • Keep the Samples around 25, and CFG around 8, but feel free to experiment!

Have fun!
